snippet.title: Mixorcist Episode 37: Howie Weinberg Mastering by Console Acustica Audio/Studio DMI/Howie Weinberg
snippet.description:
You have to hear it to believe it. Slate joked about this. Acustica Audio made it a reality. The Howie Weinberg Mastering Console. The entire studio and workflow capture in a single interface. 
All the SPL Iron, Masterbay, MMC Mastering Console, Sontec 432  mastering equalizer and Mytek, dCS converters you can handle. And yes, you can clip it. HWMC is the most accurate mastering console chain offered in plugin history.
https://www.acustica-audio.com/store/products/hwmc
Music: "Loaded" by Plastic Bag : https://open.spotify.com/track/4e3CHLqiIOGsdq9ZGX1CTu?si=d4a07f616ddc4226
